    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "u sure? it doesnt feel that bad, just a sharp ache. i dont really have a fever or anything. i'm just really tired and it's late here. if i take a higher dose of the ibuprofen it'll probably just settle it down so i can sleep. isn't that better than driving myself to the hospital in the middle of the night?",
